  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Magic Massana is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>An extensive buffet breakfast will fuel you up to start the day and when you return the evening meal is served buffet style with a wide variety of choice including show cooking or main courses cooked to order.</p>
<p>A buffet style Christmas dinner in served on Christmas Eve and a Gala Dinner on New Year's Eve with drinks included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
