  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the La Massana area of <a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal">Arinsal</a> and close to the gondola that takes you up to the ski area. Hotel Magic Massana is an ideal base for you and your group if you're looking for good value for money on your ski holiday. The hotel features some great spa facilities as well as a traditional Irish Pub which is a popular apr<span>è</span>s ski venue. </p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>Hotel Magic Massana is located in the centre of the village and getting yourself on the mountain in the morning could not be easier. The hotel is just 100 metres from the gondola which takes you directly up to the ski area and ski school meeting points. When you're not busy on the slopes, we'd recommend visiting Andorra's capital. Magic Massana is located a short 15 minute bus journey from Andorra La Vella where you'll find a huge range of shops, bars and restaurants - and the bus stop is just up the road from the hotel. To top it all off, La Massana is located in a valley with the hotel providing unbeatable panoramic views of the mountains. </p>
<h2>Spa and wellness facilities</h2>
<p>The Hotel Magic Massana offers some fantastic wellness facilities for you to enjoy. Enjoy relaxing in the indoor pool, whirlpool, steam room and a sauna. You'll also have opportunities to book a beauty treatment or massage locally and there is a free fitness room for those of you who have not already exhausted yourselves on the slopes.</p>
<h2>Ski storage included</h2>
<p>The ski hire shop is located a short distance from the hotel and you can collect your equipment upon arrival ready to hit the slopes early the next morning. You also don't have to worry about finding somewhere to store your gear as the hotel has a ski and boot storage room with designated lockers included with your stay. </p>]]></description>
