  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Magic Massana is located in the centre of La Massana and only a short 4 minutes' bus ride from Arinsal resort.</p>
<p>The hotel is also located close to the bus stop that takes you into the capital of Andorra, Andorra La Vella, which takes 15 minutes' to get to by bus.</p>
<p>It is only 1 minute's walk to the nearest ski lift (La Massana gondola) which provides direct access to the Vallnord ski area and ski school meeting points.</p>
<p> </p>]]></locationDescription>
